<style>
body {
  color: #555;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.wrap {
  width: 480px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.subhead {
  margin-top: 30px;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.stats {
  background: #eee;
}

.statItem {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 30px;
}

.statItem:first-of-type {
}

.arrow {
  font-size: 18px;
  vertical-align: middle;
}

.number {
  font-size: 36px;
  font-weight: bold;
  margin: 0;
}

.number.better {
  color: #49be5a;
}

.number.worse {
  color: #f44336;
}

.label {
  margin: 0;
  font-weight: normal;
}

.contentSection {
  text-align: left;
}

ul {
  padding: 0
}

li {
  margin: 10px 0;
}

.button {
  background: #49be5a;
  display: block;
  color: #ffffff;
  padding: 0.6em 1.5em;
  border-radius: 3px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 18px;
  margin-top: 40px;
  width: 40%;
}

</style>

<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <%= email_image_tag 'logo.png', class: 'imgClass', width: 200, style: 'margin:0;margin-top: 40px; padding:0; border:none; display:block;', alt: "logo" %>

    <h1>Weekly Summary</h1>
    <h3>What gets measured gets mananged.</h3>

    <section class="stats">
      <div class="statItem">
        <p class="number better">
        80%
        <span class="arrow">&#9650;</span>
        </p>

        <p class="label">Tasks completed</p>
      </div>

      <div class="statItem">
        <p class="number worse">
        7
        <span class="arrow">&#9660;</span>
        </p>
        <p class="label">Weekly rating</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contentSection">
      <h3 class="subhead">Efficiency and Impact</h3>
      <p>You did well completing your tasks this week, but felt you could have been more productive. Your tasks were low impact.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="contentSection">
      <h3 class="subhead">What you could have done better</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          I got sucked into a large amount of unplanned work on Nugget. I should have known to not make estimates without having the proper context. Very frustrated with myself and Sturdy right now.
