        <li>
          I planned to set up Matter's DNS and S3 without confirming that I had access to all the tools I needed.
        </li>
        <li>
          Snoozed my alarm, didn't work out, and couldn't find my focus today. I allowed myself to become distracted.
        </li>
        <li>
          Not much.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="contentSection">
      <h3 class="subhead">What you did well</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          I got sucked into a large amount of unplanned work on Nugget. I should have known to not make estimates without having the proper context. Very frustrated with myself and Sturdy right now.
        </li>
        <li>
          I planned to set up Matter's DNS and S3 without confirming that I had access to all the tools I needed.
        </li>
        <li>
          Snoozed my alarm, didn't work out, and couldn't find my focus today. I allowed myself to become distracted.
        </li>
        <li>
          Not much.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <%= link_to "Plan your week", login_url, class: "button" %>
  </div>
</body>
